description:
Jorge Badia Romero was the brother of artist Enrique Romero. They published together under the title "Hnos. Badia".

In addition to having worked in Spain in the 1950s he also worked for Warren Publishing under the name Jorge (George) Galvez and Jorge B. Galvez.
